To Install
==========

1) Find your addons directory.
	Windows: C:\Users\[JohnDoe]\AppData\Roaming\XBMC\addons
	Linux: ~/.xbmc/addons
	
2) Create a directory called plugin.video.fox.news.live

3) Drop the files from the github repo into the new directory.

4) Restart XBMC.

5) Go to Video add-ons and you should see Fox News Live.